Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Coke Studio Bharat | Kya Karie Korimol | ALIF x Aashima Mahajan x Noor Mohammad
snippet.description:
A father-daughter relationship envelops immense compassion, protection, and love. They share a special connection that grows stronger with time and never fades away. #KyaKarieKorimol unveils such a beautiful father-daughter bond on a wedding day. The lyrics tell the emotional journey of a bride and her father as they prepare for her wedding feast.

Featuring Alif, a poet, singer, and songwriter who won the IRAA Award for his single ‚ÄòLike A Sufi‚Äô, his poignant and melancholic lyrical compositions are known for their colloquial references to society.

He‚Äôs accompanied by the very soulful Aashima Mahajan, a well-known Indian musician, playback singer, and actor & Noor Mohammad, an Indian traditional Sufi music performer and songwriter from Handwara in North Kashmir.

Tune in to this masterpiece to get a glimpse of a father-daughter love.

CREDITS
 
ALIF x Aashima Mahajan x Noor Mohammad
 
Written & Composed by ALIF
Creative Producer: Ankur Tewari
Produced by Aman Moroney, ALIF & Ashish Manchanda

Tere Bin Episode 49 Teaser - 25th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Divya, IAS, Rank 105 | UPSC Topper 2022  | Hindi Medium | Mock Interview | Drishti IAS
snippet.description:
Divya has secured 105th rank in UPSC CSE exam 2022. The mock interview she has given in Drishti IAS institute has been uploaded on Drishti IAS Channel. We extend our heartiest congratulations to Divya on this great achievement. We feel immense pleasure to be a part of her beautiful journey and once again we wish her all the very best for a bright future.
As we all know that UPSC CSE Mock Interviews are a great medium to understand the various dimensions of the Personality Test conducted by UPSC. These Mock Interviews not only familiarize the aspirants with the actual process of UPSC Interviews but also help in identifying the areas that a candidate needs to work upon. Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.
We hope that this video of the UPSC IAS Mock Interview will help you understand the approach one should have to tackle the various kinds of questions asked by the panel members.

localized.title: Divya, IAS, Rank 105 | UPSC Topper 2022  | Hindi Medium | Mock Interview | Drishti IAS
localized.description:
Divya has secured 105th rank in UPSC CSE exam 2022. The mock interview she has given in Drishti IAS institute has been uploaded on Drishti IAS Channel. We extend our heartiest congratulations to Divya on this great achievement. We feel immense pleasure to be a part of her beautiful journey and once again we wish her all the very best for a bright future.
As we all know that UPSC CSE Mock Interviews are a great medium to understand the various dimensions of the Personality Test conducted by UPSC. These Mock Interviews not only familiarize the aspirants with the actual process of UPSC Interviews but also help in identifying the areas that a candidate needs to work upon. Even though one can imagine oneself in a UPSC Interview setting, it is strongly recommended that you watch these Mock Interviews and learn from the experiences of IAS toppers, so that you give your best shot when you reach the interview stage of examination.
We hope that this video of the UPSC IAS Mock Interview will help you understand the approach one should have to tackle the various kinds of questions asked by the panel members.

snippet.description:
Achara & Steph reacts to one of the legendary films of Farhan Akhtar, Bhaag Milkha Bhaag in which  Farhan Akhtar ( Zindagi Na Milegi Dobara & Dil Chahta Hai) - plays the role of Milkha Singh who is a legend in himself. This movie is a Biopic of Milka Singh which shows the truth behind the ascension of Milkha Singh, who was scarred by the India-Pakistan partition. Check out this video to see their reactions.

Mass Maharaja Ravi Teja and Vamsee‚Äôs Pan India Project #TigerNageswaraRao to be produced by Abhishek Agarwal under Abhishek Agarwal Arts and to be presented by Tej Narayan Agarwal.

Tiger Nageswara Rao will be made in Telugu, Hindi, Tamil, Kannada, and Malayalam languages. Based on the life of the notorious thief from Stuartpuram, Tiger Nageswara Rao is going to be highest budgeted film for Ravi Teja. This will mark first Pan India project of the actor.

GV Prakash Kumar will score muic for the film that has dialogues by Srikanth Vissa. R Madhie ISC will crank the camera and Avinash Kolla is the production designer. Mayank Singhaniya is the co-producer.

snippet.title: PART 2 - RAHUL DUA IN AMERICA | The HORRORS of RENTING a CAR in USA | StandUp Comedy by Rahul Dua
snippet.description:
"Oh Hello!" Australia and NZ tour (Jun'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour
"New Comedy Special 2023-24" UK-EU Tour (Aug-Sep'23) tickets: https://linktr.ee/RahulDuaTour

This video is the 2nd and the most important part of my series of jokes and observations about life in USA. 
These are observational jokes rehearsed and delivered in just 8 - 9 shows, unlike conventional stand up content which takes a couple of years to perfect. 
Since public transport is nearly absent in USA, I had to rent a car to move around. Though bad, it was the one way. This video is a real life personal account of me renting American Muscle and the horrors associated with it. Via this video I hope to convey all of my anger, surprise, shock, regret and the plethora of other emotions that I felt arising out of the massive inconvenience and hidden charges associated with US Car rental. 
Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 

#rahuldua #usa #standupcomedy #nri #comedy #jokes #carrental #taxes #dodge #americanmuscle #story  

Shot by: Yours Truly & Mehtab Singh 
Edited by Gaurav Bhatt (https://www.instagram.com/gauravbhatt101)
Sound Mixed, Mastered and Engineered by: Sreejit Menon (https://www.instagram.com/porcupinesree)
Colour Grading: Karan Asnani (Myoho Films) (https://www.instagram.com/myohofilms)
Thumbnail designed by: Hritik Singh (https://www.instagram.com/anonymous_friend7)
Transcription and subtitles by : Pavitra Nayyar (https://www.instagram.com/pavizzaa/) and Shivansh Anand (https://www.instagram.com/shivansh.mov)
Special Thanks: Anubhav Singh Bassi, Simran Singh, Imthiaz Sherriff, Sudhakar G (OHO Productions)

These are observational jokes rehearsed and delivered in just 8 - 9 shows, unlike conventional stand up content which takes a couple of years to perfect. 
Since public transport is nearly absent in USA, I had to rent a car to move around. Though bad, it was the one way. This video is a real life personal account of me renting American Muscle and the horrors associated with it. Via this video I hope to convey all of my anger, surprise, shock, regret and the plethora of other emotions that I felt arising out of the massive inconvenience and hidden charges associated with US Car rental. 
Drop in a LIKE and SHARE the video if you've had similar experiences or know someone who went through something similar, and COMMENT with your favourite joke from the video. 

#rahuldua #usa #standupcomedy #nri #comedy #jokes #carrental #taxes #dodge #americanmuscle #story

snippet.title: Barbie | Main Trailer
snippet.description:
Giant blowout party ‚úÖ
Planned choreography ‚úÖ
New #BarbieTheMovie Trailer ‚úÖ
Only in Theaters July 21.

To live in Barbie Land is to be a perfect being in a perfect place.  Unless you have a full-on existential crisis.  Or you‚Äôre a Ken.

Pre-order/save Barbie The Album: https://barbiethealbum.lnk.to/BTA

From Oscar-nominated writer/director Greta Gerwig (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúLady Bird‚Äù) comes ‚ÄúBarbie,‚Äù starring Oscar-nominees Margot Robbie (‚ÄúBombshell,‚Äù ‚ÄúI, Tonya‚Äù) and Ryan Gosling (‚ÄúLa La Land,‚Äù ‚ÄúHalf Nelson‚Äù) as Barbie and Ken, alongside America Ferrera (‚ÄúEnd of Watch,‚Äù the ‚ÄúHow to Train Your Dragon‚Äù films), Kate McKinnon (‚ÄúBombshell,‚Äù ‚ÄúYesterday‚Äù), Issa Rae (‚ÄúThe Photograph,‚Äù ‚ÄúInsecure‚Äù), Rhea Perlman (‚ÄúI‚Äôll See You in My Dreams,‚Äù ‚ÄúMatilda‚Äù), and Will Ferrell (the ‚ÄúAnchorman‚Äù films, ‚ÄúTalladega Nights‚Äù).  The film also stars Michael Cera (‚ÄúScott Pilgrim vs. the World,‚Äù ‚ÄúJuno‚Äù), Ariana Greenblatt (‚ÄúAvengers: Infinity War,‚Äù ‚Äú65‚Äù), Ana Cruz Kayne (‚ÄúLittle Women‚Äù), Emma Mackey (‚ÄúEmily,‚Äù ‚ÄúSex Education‚Äù), Hari Nef (‚ÄúAssassination Nation,‚Äù ‚ÄúTransparent‚Äù), Alexandra Shipp (the ‚ÄúX-Men‚Äù films), Kingsley Ben-Adir (‚ÄúOne Night in Miami,‚Äù ‚ÄúPeaky Blinders‚Äù), Simu Liu (‚ÄúShang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings‚Äù), Ncuti Gatwa (‚ÄúSex Education‚Äù), Scott Evans (‚ÄúGrace and Frankie‚Äù), Jamie Demetriou (‚ÄúCruella‚Äù), Connor Swindells (‚ÄúSex Education,‚Äù ‚ÄúEmma.‚Äù), Sharon Rooney (‚ÄúDumbo,‚Äù ‚ÄúJerk‚Äù), Nicola Coughlan (‚ÄúBridgerton,‚Äù ‚ÄúDerry Girls‚Äù), Ritu Arya (‚ÄúThe Umbrella Academy‚Äù), Grammy Award-winning singer/songwriter Dua Lipa and Oscar-winner Helen Mirren (‚ÄúThe Queen‚Äù).

Gerwig directed ‚ÄúBarbie‚Äù from a screenplay by Gerwig & Oscar nominee Noah Baumbach (‚ÄúMarriage Story,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Squid and the Whale‚Äù), based on Barbie by Mattel.  The film‚Äôs producers are Oscar nominee David Heyman (‚ÄúMarriage Story,‚Äù ‚ÄúGravity‚Äù), Robbie, Tom Ackerley and Robbie Brenner, with Gerwig, Baumbach, Ynon Kreiz, Richard Dickson, Michael Sharp, Josey McNamara, Courtenay Valenti, Toby Emmerich and Cate Adams serving as executive producers.

Gerwig‚Äôs creative team behind the camera included Oscar-nominated director of photography Rodrigo Prieto (‚ÄúThe Irishman,‚Äù ‚ÄúSilence,‚Äù ‚ÄúBrokeback Mountain‚Äù), six-time Oscar-nominated production designer Sarah Greenwood (‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù), editor Nick Houy (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúLady Bird‚Äù), Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù), visual effects supervisor Glen Pratt (‚ÄúPaddington 2,‚Äù ‚ÄúBeauty and the Beast‚Äù) and music supervisor George Drakoulias (‚ÄúWhite Noise,‚Äù ‚ÄúMarriage Story‚Äù), with music by Oscar winners Mark Ronson and Andrew Wyatt (‚ÄúA Star Is Born‚Äù).

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents a Heyday Films Production, a LuckyChap Entertainment Production, a NB/GG Pictures Production, a Mattel Production, ‚ÄúBarbie.‚Äù  The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and released in theaters only nationwide on July 21, 2023 and beginning internationally on July 19, 2023.

snippet.description:

A bunch of people are invited to play some mysterious game. Called in a mysterious house, every individual gets an envelope that consists of further instructions about the game. One of the participants, Rohit, gets the blank envelope and is feeling confused. A mysterious voice, which earlier guided the contestants, is heard again by Rohit who helps him procure a gun. Rohit gets the instructions of attacking someone. Who is that person? What is this game? Can CID solve this case? To know, watch the full episode.

About CID:
-----------------
Today, the first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. The plot throws up intriguing twists and turns at every stage to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Episode 3780: Alvida Popatlal
--------------------------------------------------------
 The spirit of Popatlal's departed aunt is enraged because she opposes his decision to change his name. Popatlal tries to persuade her and tells her about the arguments for changing the names. Later, she grants permission to Popatlal and blesses him. Popatlal is happy to have a dream of her late aunt as now he will get marries soon with the name 'Pyarelal. About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises

snippet.title: PM Modi's BIGGEST challenge to protect India's ECONOMY | Geopolitics by Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu expose the western hypocrisy of blaming INDIA for funding Russian invasion of Ukraine. The west has blamed India of being a "laundromat" country by helping Russia sell its crude oil to Europe. While Europe is unapologetic of its duplicity - it finds a soft target in India for all the global issues.

Abhi and Niyu is the fastest growing Indian educational YouTube channel. Abhi and Niyu are a husband-wife couple who believe in the power of our youth.

Abhi and Niyu started their page to talk about positive, impactful ideas and to inspire offline action from online content. snippet.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Reprise | Music Prod. by @BluishMusic
snippet.description:
"Boyfriend Reprise" the song offers a raw and honest plea of running away from toxicity, own thoughts, insecure nature of an individual in a relationship. This reprise version is a nonchalant expression of Dino James wherein through his powerful lyrics and emotional delivery, Dino James sheds light on an important issue that is often overlooked and ignored in our society. Dino James has a strong message for the ones who are facing such insecurities, "You shouldn't let such insecurities consume you or bother you choose to walk away and cut-off this insecurities when needed"

hi.title: Dino James - Boyfriend Reprise | Music Prod. by @BluishMusic
hi.description:
"Boyfriend Reprise" the song offers a raw and honest plea of running away from toxicity, own thoughts, insecure nature of an individual in a relationship. This reprise version is a nonchalant expression of Dino James wherein through his powerful lyrics and emotional delivery, Dino James sheds light on an important issue that is often overlooked and ignored in our society. Dino James has a strong message for the ones who are facing such insecurities, "You shouldn't let such insecurities consume you or bother you choose to walk away and cut-off this insecurities when needed"

snippet.title: The Sengol, the eternal symbol of transfer of power to India in 1947
snippet.description:
At the inauguration of the new Parliament House on 28th May 2023, PM Narendra Modi will establish the historical and sacred 'Sengol' in the Parliament House. It will be installed close to the Speaker‚Äôs podium in the Lok Sabha.

Considered as the symbol of fair and equitable governance, this is the same Sengol that was accepted by the first Prime Minister of India, Jawaharlal Nehru on the night of 14th August. It was precisely the moment in which power was transferred by the British into the hands of Indians. 

#Sengol #ParliamentHouse #AmritKaal #AKAM #PMNarendraModi #AmitShah

snippet.title: Living like Wednesday Addams for 24 hours.. *dancing like her in public*ü•≤
snippet.description:
In today's hilarious and spooky challenge, I decided to immerse myself in the world of the iconic Wednesday Addams from The Addams Family. Get ready to join me as I live, eat, and play like Wednesday Addams for a full 24 hours!

üñ§ Living Like Wednesday Addams:
From her dark sense of humor to her gothic fashion style, Wednesday Addams is a character that has captivated audiences for generations. I couldn't resist the opportunity to step into her shoes and experience a day in her peculiar and macabre world.

üçΩÔ∏è Creepy Cuisine:
To fully embrace the challenge, I had to indulge in the kinds of spooky and unconventional meals that Wednesday Addams would enjoy. Watch as I explore unusual recipes and try eerie treats that are sure to make your skin crawl!

üéÆ Spooky Games and Activities:
Wednesday Addams is known for her love of all things eerie and mysterious. Join me as I engage in some chilling games and activities that capture the essence of Wednesday's unique and dark interests. From board games with a twist to peculiar hobbies, you won't want to miss the fun!

üíÄ Fashion Transformation:
No challenge would be complete without a fashion transformation! Watch as I recreate Wednesday Addams' signature look, from her iconic braided pigtails to her monochromatic wardrobe. I'll show you how to achieve her creepy-chic style using items you may already have in your closet.


Join me on this wild and wacky adventure as I channel my inner Wednesday Addams for a full 24 hours. Get ready for laughs, scares, and plenty of bizarre moments that will keep you entertained throughout the video!

snippet.description:
Cheetah ‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§Æ‡•å‡§§ ‡§ï‡§æ ‡§ï‡•à‡§∏‡•á ‡§¨‡§¶‡§≤‡§æ ‡§≤‡•á‡§ó‡•Ä Karishma Singh || Maddam Sir - Ep.124

Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì Gulki Joshi, Shilpa Shinde, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Produced By ‚Äì Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ‡§∏‡§∞ #comedy 

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama madam and comedy
